== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2008年11月上旬，頂峰娛樂公布他們已取得[[史蒂芬妮·梅爾|史蒂芬妮·梅爾]]的《[[暮光之城系列|吸血新世紀系列]]》中其餘小說的改編權：包括[[暮光之城：新月|新月]]、[[暮光之城：蝕|蝕]]和[[暮光之城：破曉|破曉]]<ref name="Rights">{{cite news|last=Zeitchik |first=Steven |title='Twilight' film franchise looks ahead |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |publisher=[[Nielsen_Company|Nielsen Business Media]] |date=2008-11-14 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3ifc7bb2290700c27f4a0ada4363d9b59e |accessdate=2009-03-28 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081217082845/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3ifc7bb2290700c27f4a0ada4363d9b59e |archivedate=2008-12-17 }}</ref>。2009年2月，頂峰娛樂確認他們將會開始製作《蝕》。在同一天，公司宣布導演[[克里斯·魏茲|基斯·韋士]]將要在《新月》的後期製作中，同時開始拍攝《蝕》的工作，因此他不會執導第三輯電影<ref>{{cite news | author= Joshua Rich | title= 'Twilight' exclusive: Chris Weitz will not direct third film, 'Eclipse' | url= http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/02/twilight-chris.html | publisher= [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date= 2009-02-20 | accessdate= 2009-02-20 | dead-url= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090223171450/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/02/twilight-chris.html | archivedate= 2009-02-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author= Brandon Gray | title= Third 'Twilight' Dawns Summer 2010 | url= http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2550&p=.htm | publisher= [[Amazon.com|Amazon.com]] | work= [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | date= 2009-02-20 | accessdate= 2009-02-20 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090224131006/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2550&p=.htm | archive-date= 2009-02-24 | dead-url= no }}</ref>。這部電影將由導演{{le|大衛·史雷德|David Slade}}執導，{{le|梅麗莎·羅森堡|Melissa Rosenberg}}回歸擔任編劇。大衛·史雷德參與了該項目，有兩至三次分別探訪演員，以討論角色和劇情<ref>{{cite video| title = Director David Slade discusses "Eclipse"| url = http://www.makingof.com/posts/watch/1906/director-david-slade-discusses-eclipse| time = 3:39 minutes| work = MakingOf.com| access-date = 2019-11-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120407125446/http://www.makingof.com/posts/watch/1906/director-david-slade-discusses-eclipse| archive-date = 2012-04-07| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
2009年7月下旬，頂峰娛樂透露他們將會以[[布莱斯·达拉斯·霍华德|拜絲·黛麗·侯活]]取代飾演吸血鬼敵人維多利亞的原有演員{{link-en|瑞秋·拉菲佛|Rachelle Lefevre}}，他們把易角的決定歸因於計劃有衝突，拉菲佛對此作出回應，稱她對該決定感到「震驚」和「非常難過」<ref>{{cite web |title= Rachelle Lefevre 'Stunned' Over 'Eclipse' Recasting |url= http://www.accesshollywood.com/_article_21171 |work= [[Access_Hollywood|Access Hollywood]] |publisher= NBC Universal, Inc. |date= 2009-07-29 |accessdate= 2009-08-18 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090813183531/http://www.accesshollywood.com/_article_21171 |archive-date= 2009-08-13 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。侯活被邀請到《吸血新世紀》參演維多利亞一角時，她原先推辭了，因為「那部分太小了」<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwR1q-R_L3I |title= Dish Rag: Catherine Hardwicke on Bryce Dallas Howard |work= YouTube |publisher= Google.com |date=  |accessdate= 2010-06-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120831005030/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qwR1q-R_L3I |archive-date= 2012-08-31 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

《寂静岭 (电影)|鬼魅山房》的[[喬黛爾·弗蘭|喬黛爾·弗蘭]]被選為新生吸血鬼[[布莉的重生─暮光之城：蝕外傳|布莉·坦納]]<ref name="Sperling">{{cite web | author= Nicole Sperling | title= 'Twilight Saga: Eclipse' beings production today | url= http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/08/18/twilight-saga-eclipse-begins-production-today/ | work= [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date= 2009-08-18 | accessdate= 2009-08-18 | archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/66SxMKtI9?url=http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/08/18/twilight-saga-eclipse-begins-production-today/ | archive-date= 2012-03-27 | dead-url= yes }}</ref>。其他新的演員包括飾演萊利的[[薩維爾·山繆|澤維爾·塞繆]]<ref name="Samuel">{{cite web |author= Tanner Stransky |title= 'Twilight' third pic 'Eclipse' begins casting with Australian unknown Xavier Samuel |url= http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/07/twilight-third-pic-eclipse-xavier-samuel.html |publisher= [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date= 2009-07-17 |accessdate= 2009-07-18 |dead-url= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090718201859/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/07/twilight-third-pic-eclipse-xavier-samuel.html |archivedate= 2009-07-18 }}</ref>，[[傑克·休斯頓|積·赫斯頓]]飾羅伊斯·金二世<ref name="Huston">{{cite web |author= Wendy Mitchell |title= Jack Huston to play Royce King II in 'Eclipse' |url= http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/08/11/jack-huston-to-play-royce-king-ii-in-eclipse/ |publisher= Entertainment Weekly |date= 2009-08-11 |accessdate= 2009-08-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090815061130/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/08/11/jack-huston-to-play-royce-king-ii-in-eclipse/ |archive-date= 2009-08-15 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，[[凱特琳娜·桑迪諾·莫雷諾|凱特琳娜·桑迪諾·莫雷諾]]飾瑪麗亞，{{link-en|茱莉亞·鍾斯|Julia Jones}}飾演莉雅·克利爾沃特，及{{link-en|布布·史超域|Booboo Stewart}}飾演賽斯·克利爾沃特<ref name="Sperling" />。試演不同角色的演員並沒有用於工作的劇本。此外，女演員{{link-en|姬詩·普勞特|Kirsten Prout}}提到，「他們根據書中的場景製作了準確的抄本......他們沒有給出劇本。所以試聽方只是閱讀幾頁《[[暮光之城|吸血新世紀]]》，並閱讀在散佈著描述之間的台詞<ref name="iesb">{{cite web |author=Christina Radish |title=Exclusive Interview: Kirsten Prout is Lucy in The Twilight Saga: