2009年8月17日，《蝕》的主要拍攝於溫哥華電影工作室開始<ref name="filming" /><ref>{{cite web |title=''The Twilight Saga: Eclipse'' Starts Shooting |url=http://www.reelzchannel.com/movie-news/4204/the-twilight-saga-eclipse-starts-shooting |publisher=ReelzChannel |date=2009-08-18 |accessdate=2009-08-20 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090826133348/http://www.reelzchannel.com/movie-news/4204/the-twilight-saga-eclipse-starts-shooting |archivedate=2009-08-26 }}</ref>。8月29日，姬絲汀·史超域、比利·伯克及其他演員，正在拍攝戴著畢業帽和畢業禮服的場景<ref>{{cite web |url=http://twilightguide.com/tg/2009/08/29/filming-eclipse-graduation-scenes/ |title=Filming Eclipse Graduation Scenes |publisher=Twilight Guide |date=2009-08-29 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100714062139/http://twilightguide.com/tg/2009/08/29/filming-eclipse-graduation-scenes/ |archive-date=2010-07-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。9月2日，哈維爾·塞繆爾和姬絲汀·史超域及羅拔·柏迪臣一起在貝拉家的舞台上進行拍攝<ref>{{cite web |author= LMCullen |url= http://www.eclipsemovie.org/eclipse-filming-details-riley-shows-his-creepy-side-plus-new-pics-of-bryce-dallas-howard/ |title= Eclipse Filming Details: Riley Shows His Creepy Side, Plus New Pics of Bryce Dallas Howard |publisher= Eclipse Movie |date= 2009-09-03 |accessdate= 2010-06-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100618134023/http://www.eclipsemovie.org/eclipse-filming-details-riley-shows-his-creepy-side-plus-new-pics-of-bryce-dallas-howard/ |archive-date= 2010-06-18 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。導演{{le|大衛·史雷德|David Slade}}說在9月13日利用帳篷拍攝了一個場景<ref>{{cite web |author= LMCullen |url= http://www.eclipsemovie.org/eclipse-filming-details-the-tent-scene/ |title= Eclipse Filming Details: The Tent Scene |publisher= Eclipse Movie |date= 2009-09-12 |accessdate= 2010-06-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100525045329/http://www.eclipsemovie.org/eclipse-filming-details-the-tent-scene/ |archive-date= 2010-05-25 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。他還說，他們在9月17日拍攝了雅各吻貝拉的戲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.clevvertv.com/twilight-saga/5761/more-eclipse-filming-updates.html |title=More ‘Eclipse’ Filming Updates |publisher=Clevvertv.com |date=2009-09-17 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091208173810/http://www.clevvertv.com/twilight-saga/5761/more-eclipse-filming-updates.html |archive-date=2009-12-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影於2009年10月29日[[殺青|殺青]]，而後期製作則在11月下旬開始<ref name="wrapfilm" />。史雷德在他的[[Twitter|Twitter]]帳戶上發布了多個更新，聲稱編輯進展順利<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.clevvertv.com/twilight-saga/7629/eclipse-is-doing-well-in-post-production.html |title=Eclipse is Doing Well in Post-Production |publisher=Clevvertv.com |date=2009-11-15 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091119110423/http://www.clevvertv.com/twilight-saga/7629/eclipse-is-doing-well-in-post-production.html |archive-date=2009-11-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他說：「故事和他們接近電影的方法要求採取更現實的方式<ref>{{cite web |url=http://team-twilight.com/20091211/updates-eclipse-postproduction-david-slade/ |title=Updates on ‘Eclipse’ post-production from David Slade Team-Twilight | Movie News, Pics & Fan Site |publisher=Team-twilight.com |date=2009-12-11 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100501033725/http://team-twilight.com/20091211/updates-eclipse-postproduction-david-slade/ |archive-date=2010-05-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。」2010年4月，有消息指電影需要進行重新拍攝。史雷德和史蒂芬妮·梅爾與三位主角一同出現在拍攝現場<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/thedishrag/2010/05/twilight-eclipse-reshoots-with-robert-pattinson-kristen-stewart-and-taylor-lautner-were-fantastic.html |title='Twilight: Eclipse' reshoots with Robert Pattinson, Kristen Stewart and Taylor Lautner were 'fantastic' – The Dish Rag – Zap2it |publisher=[[Zap2it|Zap2it]] |date=2010-05-03 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100506061833/http://blog.zap2it.com/thedishrag/2010/05/twilight-eclipse-reshoots-with-robert-pattinson-kristen-stewart-and-taylor-lautner-were-fantastic.html |archive-date=2010-05-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2010年1月，該電影劇本的初稿在互聯網上被洩露<ref name="leak">{{cite web |author=Jocelyn Vena |title=Leaked 'Eclipse' Script Is Reportedly An Early Version |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1629168/story.jhtml |publisher=[[Viacom_(2005–present)|Viacom]] |work=MTV |date=2010-01-06 |accessdate=2010-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100115061024/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1629168/story.jhtml |archive-date=2010-01-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該劇本大概屬於參與的演員[[傑克遜·拉斯波恩|傑克遜·拉斯波恩]]，因為他的名字在每一頁上都有[[水印|水印]]標記<ref name="leak" />。

