《蝕》的門票在2010年5月14日（星期五）於各種在線電影票販上銷售<ref name="Tickets">{{cite web | author = Floydian Trip | date = 2010-05-11 | url = http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/37454/twilight-saga-eclipse-final-runtime-new-still-ticket-info | title = Twilight Saga: Eclipse Final Runtime, New Still & Ticket Info | publisher = Dreadcentral.com | accessdate = 2010-06-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100514155730/http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/37454/twilight-saga-eclipse-final-runtime-new-still-ticket-info | archive-date = 2010-05-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。電影的正式紅毯首映禮於2010年6月24日在洛杉磯諾基亞劇院（Los Angeles Nokia Theatre）舉行<ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.gossipcop.com/eclipse-premiere-june-24/ | title= Eclipse premiere | Eclipse Grauman's | Eclipse June 24 | publisher= Gossipcop.com | date= 2010-04-05 | accessdate= 2010-06-15 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100611003402/http://www.gossipcop.com/eclipse-premiere-june-24/ | archive-date= 2010-06-11 | dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Rosenfield |first=Tracy |url=http://www.hollywoodnews.com/2010/05/16/summit-entertainment-announces-camp-out-dates-for-%E2%80%9Ceclipse%E2%80%9D-premiere/ |title=Summit Entertainment Announces Camp-Out Dates for "Eclipse" Premier |publisher=HollywoodNews.com |date=2010-05-16 |accessdate=2010-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100519130025/http://www.hollywoodnews.com/2010/05/16/summit-entertainment-announces-camp-out-dates-for-%E2%80%9Ceclipse%E2%80%9D-premiere/ |archive-date=2010-05-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2010年6月23日更改地點前，粉絲可以選擇從6月21日起在洛杉磯的諾基亞廣場排隊<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/notes/the-twilight-saga/the-twilight-saga-eclipse-premiere-fan-line-and-camping-rules-regulations/10150196962550005 |title=The Twilight Saga: Eclipse Premiere – Fan Line and Camping Rules & Regulations |publisher=Facebook |date= |accessdate=2010-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127054308/https://www.facebook.com/notes/the-twilight-saga/the-twilight-saga-eclipse-premiere-fan-line-and-camping-rules-regulations/10150196962550005 |archive-date=2016-01-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[英國|英國]]的官方首映禮於2010年7月1日在[[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[萊斯特廣場|李斯特廣場]]舉行，然而[[克莉絲汀·史都華|姬絲汀·史超域]]、[[羅伯·派汀森|羅拔·柏迪臣]]及[[泰勒·洛納|泰勒·洛納]]都沒有到場<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.heatworld.com/Entertainment/Films/2010/06/Noooo-R-Pattz-WONT-be-at-the-Eclipse-UK-premiere/ |title=Noooo! R-Pattz WON'T be at the Eclipse UK premiere |publisher=Heatworld.com |accessdate=2010-06-15 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100605081000/http://www.heatworld.com/Entertainment/Films/2010/06/Noooo-R-Pattz-WONT-be-at-the-Eclipse-UK-premiere/ |archivedate=2010-06-05 }}</ref>。

