《蝕》在4,416個影院和193個IMAX屏幕上放映。據此，早期有預測指電影在發行六天之內，票房將有$1.5億美元至1.8億美元之間的收入，打破了《新月》所設下的危險局面<ref>{{cite web |last=Frankel |first=Daniel |url=http://www.thewrap.com/movies/article/box-office-eclipse-blocks-out-least-150m-18835 |title=Box Office: 'Eclipse' Looks to Scare Up at Least $150M |publisher=TheWrap.com |date= |accessdate=2010-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100630085811/http://www.thewrap.com/movies/article/box-office-eclipse-blocks-out-least-150m-18835 |archive-date=2010-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Finke |first=Nikki |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/06/eclipse-top-advance-ticket-seller-of-year/ |title=‘Eclipse’ Top Advance Ticket Seller Of Year – |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2010-06-24 |accessdate=2010-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100628005703/http://www.deadline.com/2010/06/eclipse-top-advance-ticket-seller-of-year |archive-date=2010-06-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《蝕》佔Fandango網上門票銷量的82％，在2010年5月14日達到前五名。門票網站{{le|MovieTickets.com|MovieTickets.com}}指《蝕》成為了該網站上預售門票數量最高的賣方，佔每日門票銷售量超過50%<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/twilightrsquos-eclipse-tops-advance-ticket-sales-for-2010-2013470.html |title=Twilight’s 'Eclipse' tops advance ticket sales for 2010 – Films, Arts & Entertainment |publisher=The Independent |date=2010-06-29 |accessdate=2010-06-29 |location=London |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100702122045/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/twilightrsquos-eclipse-tops-advance-ticket-sales-for-2010-2013470.html |archive-date=2010-07-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2010年6月，這部電影是票房最高的賣家<ref>{{cite web |last=Bierly |first=Mandi |url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/06/25/eclipse-advance-ticket-sales-hot/ |title='Eclipse' now 2010's top advance ticket-seller | EW.com |publisher=Popwatch.ew.com |date=2010-06-25 |accessdate=2010-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100629101404/http://popwatch.ew.com/2010/06/25/eclipse-advance-ticket-sales-hot/ |archive-date=2010-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這部電影的早期票務銷售也打破了「金級電影院」的記錄，有超過8,500名《吸血新世紀》粉絲預訂了票；在《Fairview》，德克薩斯州的銷售點在6月30日售罄了《蝕》的放映門票<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/twilight-saga-eclipse-draws-record-advance-ticket-sales-for-gold-class-cinemas-97341234.html |title='Twilight Saga: Eclipse' Draws Record Advance Ticket Sales for Gold Class Cinemas – LOS ANGELES |location=California |work=PRNewswire |date=2010-06-28 |accessdate=2010-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100826080410/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/twilight-saga-eclipse-draws-record-advance-ticket-sales-for-gold-class-cinemas-97341234.html |archive-date=2010-08-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

